name: Import.SQL.CfgDateString PRUEBA 5
query:
--TODO ESTO ES UNA PRUEBA DE ACTUALIZACION DE IMPORTS 
 SELECT DISTINCT 
  dt_val::date AS fecha,
  TO_CHAR(dt_val, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS fechaString,
  EXTRACT(DOW FROM dt_val) AS DiaSemana,
  CASE 
    WHEN dt_val::date >= (CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '1 month')::date THEN 0
    ELSE 1
  END AS Enable
FROM (
  SELECT 
    '1900-01-01'::date + value AS dt_val
  FROM (
    SELECT 
      (v2 * 100 + v1 * 10 + v0) AS value
    FROM (
      SELECT 0 AS v0 UNION SELECT 1 UNION SELECT 2 UNION SELECT 3 UNION SELECT 4 
      UNION SELECT 5 UNION SELECT 6 UNION SELECT 7 UNION SELECT 8 UNION SELECT 9
    ) AS rs0
    CROSS JOIN (
      SELECT 0 AS v1 UNION SELECT 1 UNION SELECT 2 UNION SELECT 3 UNION SELECT 4 
      UNION SELECT 5 UNION SELECT 6 UNION SELECT 7 UNION SELECT 8 UNION SELECT 9
    ) AS rs1
    CROSS JOIN (
      SELECT 0 AS v2 UNION SELECT 1 UNION SELECT 2 UNION SELECT 3 UNION SELECT 4 
      UNION SELECT 5 UNION SELECT 6 UNION SELECT 7 UNION SELECT 8 UNION SELECT 9
    ) AS rs2
  ) AS rs
) AS dates
WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM dt_val) < EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) + 2;
